headline: The AI Summit New York Announces 2025 Speakers and Presenters Driving the Next Decade of AI Innovation
summary: NEW YORK, November 20, 2025--The AI Summit New York today announced its 2025 speaker lineup, featuring the brightest minds in artificial intelligence, technology and global business. The 10th edition of the show takes place at the Javits Convention Center on December 10 - 11, connecting business leaders with AI practitioners at every level.

headline: A Look at eBay's (EBAY) Valuation Following Recent Share Price Decline
summary: Shares of eBay (EBAY) have been on a downward trend over the past month, sliding roughly 15%. Investors are taking a close look at what might be driving this recent stretch, especially in the context of the stock’s year-to-date gains. See our latest analysis for eBay. Despite the recent pullback, eBay’s 30.5% share price return year-to-date reflects a strong run in 2024. Its 1-year total shareholder return of 35.8% shows solid long-term momentum.
